Simple Real-Time Example

Imagine building a Watch Chatbot.

Customer asks:

"Show me Titan watches under ₹5000 with a leather strap."

Without LangChain:

User
   │
   ▼
LLM
   │
   ▼
May guess the answer

Without product data, the answer may be incorrect.

With LangChain:

User
   │
   ▼
LangChain
   │
   ├── Reads PDF
   ├── Searches FAISS
   ├── Retrieves Watch Details
   └── Sends Context to LLM
           │
           ▼
      Accurate Answer
