What Can LangChain Connect?
=========================

| Component                | Purpose                         |
| ------------------------ | ------------------------------- |
| LLM (GPT, Gemini, Llama) | Generate responses              |
| PDF Files                | Read documents                  |
| FAISS                    | Retrieve similar information    |
| ChromaDB                 | Store document vectors          |
| Pinecone                 | Cloud vector database           |
| SQL Database             | Query structured data           |
| APIs                     | Weather, Maps, Payments, etc.   |
| Memory                   | Remember conversations          |
| Tools                    | Calculator, Search, Email, etc. |


Main Components of LangChain
===========================

| Component           | Purpose                            |
| ------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| **LLM**             | Generates answers                  |
| **Prompt Template** | Creates better prompts             |
| **Retriever**       | Retrieves relevant documents       |
| **Vector Database** | Stores embeddings                  |
| **Memory**          | Remembers conversation history     |
| **Chains**          | Connects multiple steps together   |
| **Agents**          | Decide which tool to use           |
| **Tools**           | Calculator, Search, APIs, Database |


